description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a decontamination operational Manager to work within the Sterile Services Departments at East Suffolk and North Essex Hospitals Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position available is:- 1 x 37.5 Monday to Friday&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will join a busy friendly team, dealing with all aspects of the decontamination production process &amp; procedures required for the distribution of equipment to theatres, internal wards, clinics external GP’s and Health Centers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The applicant must be able to demonstrate;-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication &amp; interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent customer services attributes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good numeracy and literacy skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good retentive memory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before applying, please ensure you view the job description, or for an informal discussion please contact Daniel Imoh the Trust Decontamination lead on 01206742471&lt;/p&gt;
